        "text": "MiroShark merged a pure-stdlib SVG renderer that turns every simulation's belief trajectory into an embeddable <img> tag — no JavaScript, no resolution choice, works in Notion, Substack, Ghost, GitHub READMEs, and LaTeX. Separately, SMTP completion emails complete the four-channel notification quadrant (webhook + Discord + Slack + email), meaning any operator with a mailbox can receive sim results with zero platform dependency. 25-PR zero-dep streak."
